snippet.title: Doko Demo Issyo (PS1) - Actual PlayStation Hardware
snippet.description: Here's the first 30 minutes of Doko Demo Issyo for PS1 played via a PS2.  UK machine was used with Tonyhax to load the retail disc with an actual pocketstation in machine.
